*) Check if this is the lastest version before you run any script:
   http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/downloads/list

*) Please do read the installation guide before you run any script
   shipped within iRedMail:
   - English: http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation
   - Chinese: http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/wiki/Installation_zh

*) Issue tracker & bug report:
   http://code.google.com/p/iredmail/issues/list

*) Wiki page (include step-by-step tutorial):
   http://www.iredmail.org/wiki/

*) Community:
   Chinese: http://www.iredmail.org/bbs/
   International: http://groups.google.com/p/iredmail/

*) Quick Installation Guide:

   # cd /path/to/iRedMail-x.y.z/
   # cd pkgs/
   # sh get_all.sh
   # cd ../
   # sh iRedMail.sh
